      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to an exacting standard. This vehicle is offered in pristine condition, reflecting a level of care that ensures both mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection. From its flawless exterior to its meticulously preserved interior, this unit represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector or enthusiast who prioritizes uncompromising quality.",
