    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it\u2019s been pampered with regular detailing. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
