    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to produce a seamless power delivery to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring precise torque vectoring. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented rod bearing replacement and a proactively reinforced rear subframe to address chassis fatigue common to the platform. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers, preserving the original kinematics and steering feedback. Finished in concours-level paint with a pristine interior, this is a turnkey example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
